com.jdroid.java.repository

Interface Repository<T extends Identifiable>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - This is a parameterized interface.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DeviceGroupRepository, DeviceRepository, FileEntityRepository, RandomRepository<T>, SynchronizedRepository<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractHibernateRepository, DebugLogsRepository, DeviceGroupHibernateRepository, DeviceHibernateRepository, FileEntityHibernateRepository, InMemoryRepository, MapRepository, MySQLHibernateRepository, SQLiteRepository, StringEntityRepository, SynchronizedInMemoryRepository

    public interface Repository<T extends Identifiable>
    Interface that all repositories must adhere to. It provides basic repository functionality.
